Father Lehi came from the time of Jeremiah he and Jeremiah warned the 
people "REPENT OR KING NEBUCHADNEZZAR KING OF BABYLON WILL TAKE YOU 
CAPTIVE!" they did not listen they stoned him. one night days before King 
Nebuchadnezzar King of Babylon came the Lord appeared to Father Lehi and 
told him to pack up everything and run the Lord will show the way for them 
to reach America. Father Lehi packed up his belongings left his gold and 
took his family and left. (two of his sons had second thoughts and wanted 
to stay)     ï»¿